==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Authorship
<hw>Au"thor*ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality or
state of being an author; function or dignity of an author.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Source; origin; origination; <as>as, the
<ex>authorship</ex> of a book or review, or of an act, or state of
affairs</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Authotype</ent>⟦br⟧
